alversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group `runtime` informer accessor |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | `v1alpha1` informer accessors |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | AgentRuntime informer + constructor |\n| `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter informer + constructor |\n| `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` | Small factory interface + `NewInformerFunc`, `TweakListOptionsFunc` |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeLister`, namespace lister |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterLister`, namespace lister |\n| `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Lister expansion interfaces |\n\n**Regeneration:** `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` (`k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1, `--with-watch`, output package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`).\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Client Errors\n\n| Error Type | Description | Handling |\n|------------|-------------|----------|\n| `IsAlreadyExists()` | Resource already exists (Create) | Retry with different name or GET existing |\n| `IsNotFound()` | Resource does not exist (Get/Update/Delete) | Check if needs Create first |\n| `IsConflict()` | Resource version mismatch (Update) | Fetch latest and retry |\n| `IsTimeout()` | Operation timed out | Retry with exponential backoff |\n| `IsServerTimeout()` | Server returned 504 | Retry |\n| `IsBadRequest()` | Invalid request body | Fix validation before retry |\n\n### Informer Errors\n\n| Scenario | Behavior |\n|----------|----------|\n| List/Watch failure | Log error, re-queue with backoff |\n| Cache sync failure | `WaitForCacheSync` returns false |\n| Graceful shutdown | `Shutdown()` stops all informers |\n\n### Common Patterns\n\n```go\n// Retry with backoff\nfunc withRetry(fn func() error) error {\n    var lastErr error\n    for i := 0; i < 3; i++ {\n        if err := fn(); err != nil {\n            if errors.IsRetryable(err) {\n                lastErr = err\n                time.Sleep(time.Duration(i+1) * time.Second)\n                continue\n            }\n            return err\n        }\n        return nil\n    }\n    return lastErr\n}\n\n// Handle conflict\nfunc updateWithRetry(ctx context.Context, client typedInterface, name string, updateFunc func(*T) *T) (*T, error) {\n    for {\n        current, err := client.Get(ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n        if err != nil {\n            return nil, err\n        }\n        updated := updateFunc(current)\n        result, err := client.Update(ctx, updated, metav1.UpdateOptions{})\n        if errors.IsConflict(err) {\n            continue // retry with fresh version\n        }\n        return result, err\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Component | Test Approach |\n|-----------|----------------|\n| Typed clients | Mock REST interface, verify request paths |\n| Listers | Populate indexer, verify List/Get methods |\n| Informers | Use fake client, verify event handlers |\n| Fake clients | Verify method signatures match interfaces |\n\n### Fake Client Usage\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/fake\"\n)\n\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeController(t *testing.T) {\n    // Create fake clients\n    k8s := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n    agentcube := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n    \n    // Pre-populate resources\n    agentcube.AgentRuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(ctx, &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test-runtime\"},\n        Spec:       runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{...},\n    }, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n    \n    // Test controller logic\n    controller := NewController(k8s, agentcube)\n    // ... assertions\n}\n```\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test Type | Environment | Notes |\n|-----------|-------------|-------|\n| E2E | Kind cluster with CRDs installed | Use envtest or actual cluster |\n| Contract | Verify generated code matches API spec | Compare against handwritten stubs |\n\n### Test Helpers\n\n| Function | Purpose |\n|----------|---------|\n| `NewFakeClientset()` | Creates in-memory clientset |\n| `NewFakeRuntimeClient()` | Typed runtime client |\n| `NewFakeInformer()` | Pre-populated informer |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Relationships\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                        Clientset                             │\n│  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │ DiscoveryClient │    │   RuntimeV1alpha1Client        │ │\n│  └─────────────────┘    │  ┌──────────┐  ┌─────────────┐ │ │\n│                         │  │AgentRun- │  │CodeInterpr- │ │ │\n│                         │  │times     │  │eter        │ │ │\n│                         │  └──────────┘  └─────────────┘ │ │\n│                         └────────────────────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n         ┌────────────────────┼────────────────────┐\n         ▼                    ▼                    ▼\n┌─────────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐\n│ SharedInformer  │  │   Listers   │  │   Controllers    │\n│ Factory         │  │             │  │   (workloadmgr)  │\n│ ┌─────────────┐ │  │ ┌─────────┐ │  └──────────────────┘\n│ │AgentRuntime │ │  │ │AgentRun-│ │\n│ │Informer     │ │  │ │times    │ │\n│ └─────────────┘ │  │ │Lister   │ │\n│ ┌─────────────┐ │  │ └─────────┘ │  ┌──────────────────┐\n│ │CodeInterp   │ │  │ ┌─────────┐ │  │   Router        │\n│ │Informer     │ │  │ │CodeIn-  │ │  └──────────────────┘\n│ └─────────────┘ │  │ │terpreter│ │\n└─────────────────┘  │ │Lister   │ │\n                      │ └─────────┘ │\n                      └─────────────┘\n```\n\n### Data Flow\n\n1. **Controller** creates/updates CR objects via typed client\n2. **Clientset** sends REST requests to API server\n3. **Informer** watches for changes, populates local cache\n4. **Lister** provides cached lookups without API server calls\n5. **Status subresource** allows separate status updates\n","additions":157,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/deployment/client-go.md","time":{"start":1775840166697,"end":1775840166718}}}}
